Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我來晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我出發了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好的 拜託妳了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要把開膛手傑克…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好 出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍微放輕鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,之後我們可是要當誘餌的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力的
